Package org.emrick.project.effect

Class RFTriggerGUI

java.lang.Object
org.emrick.project.effect.RFTriggerGUI
public class RFTriggerGUI extends Object
This class really just sets up a button to create an RF trigger. If there's already an RF trigger on the current count, then set up a delete button. If there's not, then set up a create button.
